        <abstract> 
<p>On THH’s lecture at Royal Institution ["On species and races, and their origin", <hi rend="italic">Not. Proc. R. Inst. G. B.</hi> 3 (1858–62): 195–200]. Praises eloquence of his conclusion.</p>  
<p>Has sent first part of German translation of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> to THH.</p> 
